title: A strange group of wizards visited me

author: MiniWarGaming
description:
Yes, a Guardsman needs a place to sleep that isn't a crate or barrel!  See more at MiniWarGaming.com/perdition

With the Depths of Perdition, players can create immersive sci-fi environments—starship decks, fortified shelters, test facilities, mechanical worksites, and more. The system emphasizes mood and storytelling, turning every setup into a place that feels authentic and full of dramatic energy.

Everything is based on a six-inch modular tile format that connects seamlessly and stays perfectly aligned. You can swap pieces to create new maps fast—tight runs, broad walkways, large interior zones, stacked complexes, or entire bases. The models are all supportless, printer-optimized, and built to expand.
title: Bedrooms in Warhammer?  Only in the Depths of Perdition
